I/flutter ( 6261): [00:45:41.177] ERROR [FlutterError] Flutter error:     Tried to use context.select inside a SliverList/SliderGridView.
I/flutter ( 6261): 
I/flutter ( 6261):     This is likely a mistake, as instead of rebuilding only the item that cares
I/flutter ( 6261):     about the selected value, this would rebuild the entire list/grid.
I/flutter ( 6261): 
I/flutter ( 6261):     To fix, add a `Builder` or extract the content of `itemBuilder` in a separate widget:
I/flutter ( 6261): 
I/flutter ( 6261):     ```dart
I/flutter ( 6261):     ListView.builder(
I/flutter ( 6261):       itemBuilder: (context, index) {
I/flutter ( 6261):         return Builder(builder: (context) {
I/flutter ( 6261):           final todo = context.select((TodoList list) => list[index]);
I/flutter ( 6261):           return Text(todo.name);

I/flutter ( 6261): [00:45:41.458] INFO  Received message: (message_id, result, partial)
I/flutter ( 6261): [00:45:41.482] ERROR [FlutterError] Flutter error:     Tried to use context.select inside a SliverList/SliderGridView.
I/flutter ( 6261): 
I/flutter ( 6261):     This is likely a mistake, as instead of rebuilding only the item that cares
I/flutter ( 6261):     about the selected value, this would rebuild the entire list/grid.
I/flutter ( 6261): 
I/flutter ( 6261):     To fix, add a `Builder` or extract the content of `itemBuilder` in a separate widget:
I/flutter ( 6261): 
I/flutter ( 6261):     ```dart
I/flutter ( 6261):     ListView.builder(
I/flutter ( 6261):       itemBuilder: (context, index) {
I/flutter ( 6261):         return Builder(builder: (context) {
I/flutter ( 6261):           final todo = context.select((TodoList list) => list[index]);
I/flutter ( 6261):           return Text(todo.name);
I/flutter ( 6261):         });
I/flutter ( 6261):       },
